name: bulbasaur
flavorText: A strange seed wasplanted on itsback at birth.The plant sproutsand grows withthis POKéMON.

name: ivysaur
flavorText: When the bulb onits back growslarge, it appearsto lose theability to standon its hind legs.

name: venusaur
flavorText: The plant bloomswhen it isabsorbing solarenergy. It stayson the move toseek sunlight.

name: charmander
flavorText: Obviously prefershot places. Whenit rains, steamis said to spoutfrom the tip ofits tail.

name: charmeleon
flavorText: When it swingsits burning tail,it elevates thetemperature tounbearably highlevels.

name: charizard
flavorText: Spits fire thatis hot enough tomelt boulders.Known to causeforest firesunintentionally.

name: squirtle
flavorText: After birth, itsback swells andhardens into ashell. Powerfullysprays foam fromits mouth.

name: wartortle
flavorText: Often hides inwater to stalkunwary prey. Forswimming fast, itmoves its ears tomaintain balance.

name: blastoise
flavorText: A brutal POKéMONwith pressurizedwater jets on itsshell. They areused for highspeed tackles.

name: caterpie
flavorText: Its short feet are tipped with suctionpads that enable it to tirelessly climbslopes and walls.

name: metapod
flavorText: This POKéMON isvulnerable toattack while itsshell is soft,exposing its weakand tender body.

name: butterfree
flavorText: In battle, itflaps its wingsat high speed torelease highlytoxic dust intothe air.

name: weedle
flavorText: Often found inforests, eatingleaves.It has a sharpvenomous stingeron its head.

name: kakuna
flavorText: Almost incapableof moving, thisPOKéMON can onlyharden its shellto protect itselffrom predators.

name: beedrill
flavorText: It has three poisonous stingers on its forelegs andits tail. They are used to jab its enemy repeatedly.

name: pidgey
flavorText: A common sight inforests and woods.It flaps itswings at groundlevel to kick upblinding sand.

name: pidgeotto
flavorText: Very protectiveof its sprawlingterritorial area,this POKéMON willfiercely peck atany intruder.

name: pidgeot
flavorText: When hunting, itskims the surfaceof water at highspeed to pick offunwary prey suchas MAGIKARP.

name: rattata
flavorText: Bites anythingwhen it attacks.Small and veryquick, it is acommon sight inmany places.

name: raticate
flavorText: It uses its whis­kers to maintainits balance.It apparentlyslows down ifthey are cut off.

name: spearow
flavorText: It flaps its small wings busily tofly. Using its beak, it searchesin grass for prey.

name: fearow
flavorText: With its huge andmagnificent wings,it can keep aloftwithout everhaving to landfor rest.

name: ekans
flavorText: Moves silentlyand stealthily.Eats the eggs ofbirds, such asPIDGEY andSPEAROW, whole.

name: arbok
flavorText: It is rumored thatthe ferociouswarning markingson its bellydiffer from areato area.

name: pikachu
flavorText: When several ofthese POKéMONgather, theirelectricity couldbuild and causelightning storms.

name: raichu
flavorText: Its long tail serves as a ground to protect itselffrom its own high-voltage power.

name: sandshrew
flavorText: Burrows deepunderground inarid locationsfar from water.It only emergesto hunt for food.

name: sandslash
flavorText: Curls up into aspiny ball whenthreatened. Itcan roll whilecurled up toattack or escape.

name: nidoran-f
flavorText: Although small,its venomousbarbs render thisPOKéMON dangerous.The female hassmaller horns.

name: nidorina
flavorText: The female's horndevelops slowly.Prefers physicalattacks such asclawing andbiting.

name: nidoqueen
flavorText: Its hard scalesprovide strongprotection. Ituses its heftybulk to executepowerful moves.

name: nidoran-m
flavorText: Stiffens its earsto sense danger.The larger itshorns, the morepowerful itssecreted venom.

name: nidorino
flavorText: An aggressivePOKéMON that isquick to attack.The horn on itshead secretes apowerful venom.

name: nidoking
flavorText: It uses itspowerful tail inbattle to smash,constrict, thenbreak the prey'sbones.

name: clefairy
flavorText: Its magical andcute appeal hasmany admirers.It is rare andfound only incertain areas.

name: clefable
flavorText: A timid fairyPOKéMON that israrely seen. Itwill run and hidethe moment itsenses people.

name: vulpix
flavorText: At the time ofbirth, it hasjust one tail.The tail splitsfrom its tip asit grows older.

name: ninetales
flavorText: Very smart andvery vengeful.Grabbing one ofits many tailscould result in a1000-year curse.

name: jigglypuff
flavorText: When its huge eyeslight up, it singsa mysteriouslysoothing melodythat lulls itsenemies to sleep.

name: wigglytuff
flavorText: The body is softand rubbery. Whenangered, it willsuck in air andinflate itself toan enormous size.

name: zubat
flavorText: Forms colonies inperpetually darkplaces. Usesultrasonic wavesto identify andapproach targets.

name: golbat
flavorText: Once it strikes,it will not stopdraining energyfrom the victimeven if it getstoo heavy to fly.

name: oddish
flavorText: During the day,it keeps its faceburied in theground. At night,it wanders aroundsowing its seeds.

name: gloom
flavorText: The fluid thatoozes from itsmouth isn't drool.It is a nectarthat is used toattract prey.

name: vileplume
flavorText: It has the world’s largest petals. With every step,the petals shake out heavy clouds of toxic pollen.

name: paras
flavorText: Burrows to sucktree roots. Themushrooms on itsback grow by draw­ing nutrients fromthe bug host.

name: parasect
flavorText: A host-parasitepair in which theparasite mushroomhas taken over thehost bug. Prefersdamp places.

name: venonat
flavorText: Lives in theshadows of talltrees where iteats insects. Itis attracted bylight at night.

name: venomoth
flavorText: The dustlike scales covering its wingsare color-coded to indicate the kinds ofpoison it has.

name: diglett
flavorText: Lives about oneyard undergroundwhere it feeds onplant roots. Itsometimes appearsabove ground.

name: dugtrio
flavorText: A team of DIGLETTtriplets.It triggers hugeearthquakes byburrowing 60 milesunderground.

name: meowth
flavorText: It washes its face regularly to keep the coin onits forehead spotless. It doesn’t get along withGalarian Meowth.

name: persian
flavorText: Although its furhas many admirers,it is tough toraise as a petbecause of itsfickle meanness.

name: psyduck
flavorText: While lulling itsenemies with itsvacant look, thiswily POKéMON willuse psychokineticpowers.

name: golduck
flavorText: Often seen swim­ming elegantly bylake shores. Itis often mistakenfor the Japanesemonster, Kappa.

name: mankey
flavorText: Extremely quick toanger. It couldbe docile onemoment thenthrashing awaythe next instant.

name: primeape
flavorText: Always furiousand tenacious toboot. It will notabandon chasingits quarry untilit is caught.

name: growlithe
flavorText: Very protectiveof its territory.It will bark andbite to repelintruders fromits space.

name: arcanine
flavorText: A POKéMON thathas been admiredsince the pastfor its beauty.It runs agilelyas if on wings.

name: poliwag
flavorText: Its newly grownlegs prevent itfrom running. Itappears to preferswimming thantrying to stand.

name: poliwhirl
flavorText: Capable of livingin or out ofwater. When outof water, itsweats to keepits body slimy.

name: poliwrath
flavorText: An adept swimmerat both the frontcrawl and breaststroke. Easilyovertakes the besthuman swimmers.

name: abra
flavorText: Using its abilityto read minds, itwill identifyimpending dangerand TELEPORT tosafety.

name: kadabra
flavorText: It emits specialalpha waves fromits body thatinduce headachesjust by beingclose by.

name: alakazam
flavorText: Its brain can out­perform a super­computer.Its intelligencequotient is saidto be 5,000.

name: machop
flavorText: Loves to buildits muscles.It trains in allstyles of martialarts to becomeeven stronger.

name: machoke
flavorText: Its muscular bodyis so powerful, itmust wear a powersave belt to beable to regulateits motions.

name: machamp
flavorText: Using its heavymuscles, it throwspowerful punchesthat can send thevictim clear overthe horizon.

name: bellsprout
flavorText: A carnivorousPOKéMON that trapsand eats bugs.It uses its rootfeet to soak upneeded moisture.

name: weepinbell
flavorText: It spits outPOISONPOWDER toimmobilize theenemy and thenfinishes it witha spray of ACID.

name: victreebel
flavorText: Said to live inhuge coloniesdeep in jungles,although no onehas ever returnedfrom there.

name: tentacool
flavorText: Drifts in shallowseas. Anglers whohook them byaccident areoften punished byits stinging acid.

name: tentacruel
flavorText: The tentacles arenormally keptshort. On hunts,they are extendedto ensnare andimmobilize prey.

name: geodude
flavorText: Found in fieldsand mountains.Mistaking themfor boulders,people often stepor trip on them.

name: graveler
flavorText: Rolls down slopesto move. It rollsover any obstaclewithout slowingor changing itsdirection.

name: golem
flavorText: Its boulder-likebody is extremelyhard. It caneasily withstanddynamite blastswithout damage.

name: ponyta
flavorText: Its hooves are 10times harder thandiamonds. It cantrample anythingcompletely flatin little time.

name: rapidash
flavorText: Very competitive,this POKéMON willchase anythingthat moves fastin the hopes ofracing it.

name: slowpoke
flavorText: Incredibly slowand dopey. Ittakes 5 secondsfor it to feelpain when underattack.

name: slowbro
flavorText: The SHELLDER thatis latched ontoSLOWPOKE's tailis said to feedon the host's leftover scraps.

name: magnemite
flavorText: Uses anti-gravityto stay suspended.Appears withoutwarning and usesTHUNDER WAVE andsimilar moves.

name: magneton
flavorText: Formed by severalMAGNEMITEs linkedtogether. Theyfrequently appearwhen sunspotsflare up.

name: farfetchd
flavorText: The sprig ofgreen onions itholds is itsweapon. It isused much like ametal sword.

name: doduo
flavorText: A bird that makesup for its poorflying with itsfast foot speed.Leaves giantfootprints.

name: dodrio
flavorText: Uses its threebrains to executecomplex plans.While two headssleep, one headstays awake.

name: seel
flavorText: The protrudinghorn on its headis very hard.It is used forbashing throughthick ice.

name: dewgong
flavorText: Stores thermalenergy in itsbody. Swims at asteady 8 knotseven in intenselycold waters.

name: grimer
flavorText: Appears in filthyareas. Thrives bysucking uppolluted sludgethat is pumpedout of factories.

name: muk
flavorText: Thickly coveredwith a filthy,vile sludge. Itis so toxic, evenits footprintscontain poison.

name: shellder
flavorText: Its hard shellrepels any kindof attack.It is vulnerableonly when itsshell is open.

name: cloyster
flavorText: When attacked, itlaunches itshorns in quickvolleys. Itsinnards havenever been seen.

name: gastly
flavorText: Almost invisible,this gaseousPOKéMON cloaksthe target andputs it to sleepwithout notice.

name: haunter
flavorText: Because of itsability to slipthrough blockwalls, it is saidto be from an­other dimension.

name: gengar
flavorText: Under a full moon,this POKéMONlikes to mimicthe shadows ofpeople and laughat their fright.

name: onix
flavorText: As it grows, thestone portions ofits body hardento become similarto a diamond, butcolored black.

name: drowzee
flavorText: Puts enemies tosleep then eatstheir dreams.Occasionally getssick from eatingbad dreams.

name: hypno
flavorText: When it locks eyeswith an enemy, itwill use a mix ofPSI moves such asHYPNOSIS andCONFUSION.

name: krabby
flavorText: Its pincers arenot only powerfulweapons, they areused for balancewhen walkingsideways.

name: kingler
flavorText: The large pincerhas 10000 hp ofcrushing power.However, its hugesize makes itunwieldy to use.

name: voltorb
flavorText: Usually found inpower plants.Easily mistakenfor a POKé BALL,they have zappedmany people.

name: electrode
flavorText: It stores electricenergy under veryhigh pressure.It often explodeswith little or noprovocation.

name: exeggcute
flavorText: Often mistakenfor eggs.When disturbed,they quicklygather and attackin swarms.

name: exeggutor
flavorText: Legend has it thaton rare occasions,one of its headswill drop off andcontinue on as anEXEGGCUTE.

name: cubone
flavorText: Because it neverremoves its skullhelmet, no onehas ever seenthis POKéMON'sreal face.

name: marowak
flavorText: The bone it holdsis its key weapon.It throws thebone skillfullylike a boomerangto KO targets.

name: hitmonlee
flavorText: When in a hurry,its legs lengthenprogressively.It runs smoothlywith extra long,loping strides.

name: hitmonchan
flavorText: While apparentlydoing nothing, itfires punches inlightning fastvolleys that areimpossible to see.

name: lickitung
flavorText: Its tongue can beextended like achameleon's. Itleaves a tinglingsensation when itlicks enemies.

name: koffing
flavorText: Because it storesseveral kinds oftoxic gases inits body, it isprone to explodingwithout warning.

name: weezing
flavorText: Where two kindsof poison gasesmeet, 2 KOFFINGscan fuse into aWEEZING over manyyears.

name: rhyhorn
flavorText: A POKéMON with aone-track mind.Once it charges, it won't stoprunning until itfalls asleep.

name: rhydon
flavorText: Protected by anarmor-like hide,it is capable ofliving in moltenlava of 3,600degrees.

name: chansey
flavorText: A rare and elusivePOKéMON that issaid to bringhappiness to thosewho manage to getit.

name: tangela
flavorText: The whole body isswathed with widevines that aresimilar to sea­weed. Its vinesshake as it walks.

name: kangaskhan
flavorText: The infant rarelyventures out ofits mother'sprotective pouchuntil it is 3years old.

name: horsea
flavorText: Known to shootdown flying bugswith precisionblasts of inkfrom the surfaceof the water.

name: seadra
flavorText: Capable of swim­ming backwards byrapidly flappingits wing-likepectoral fins andstout tail.

name: goldeen
flavorText: Its tail finbillows like anelegant ballroomdress, giving itthe nickname ofthe Water Queen.

name: seaking
flavorText: In the autumn spawning season, they canbe seen swimming powerfully up rivers andcreeks.

name: staryu
flavorText: If its body is torn, it can growback if the red core remains.The core flashes at midnight.

name: starmie
flavorText: Its central coreglows with theseven colors ofthe rainbow. Somepeople value thecore as a gem.

name: mr-mime
flavorText: If interruptedwhile it ismiming, it willslap around theoffender with itsbroad hands.

name: scyther
flavorText: With ninja-likeagility and speed,it can create theillusion thatthere is morethan one.

name: jynx
flavorText: It seductivelywiggles its hipsas it walks. Itcan cause peopleto dance inunison with it.

name: electabuzz
flavorText: Normally foundnear power plants,they can wanderaway and causemajor blackoutsin cities.

name: magmar
flavorText: Its body alwaysburns with anorange glow thatenables it tohide perfectlyamong flames.

name: pinsir

name: tauros
flavorText: When it targetsan enemy, itcharges furiouslywhile whipping itsbody with itslong tails.

name: magikarp
flavorText: In the distantpast, it wassomewhat strongerthan the horriblyweak descendantsthat exist today.

name: gyarados
flavorText: Once it begins to rampage, aGYARADOS will burn everythingdown, even in a harsh storm.

name: lapras
flavorText: A POKéMON thathas been over­hunted almost toextinction. Itcan ferry peopleacross the water.

name: ditto
flavorText: Capable of copyingan enemy's geneticcode to instantlytransform itselfinto a duplicateof the enemy.

name: eevee
flavorText: Its genetic codeis irregular.It may mutate ifit is exposed toradiation fromelement STONEs.

name: vaporeon
flavorText: Lives close towater. Its longtail is ridgedwith a fin whichis often mistakenfor a mermaid's.

name: jolteon

name: flareon
flavorText: When storingthermal energy inits body, itstemperature couldsoar to over 1600degrees.

name: porygon
flavorText: A POKéMON thatconsists entirelyof programmingcode. Capable ofmoving freely incyberspace.

name: omanyte
flavorText: Although longextinct, in rarecases, it can begeneticallyresurrected fromfossils.

name: omastar
flavorText: A prehistoricPOKéMON that diedout when itsheavy shell madeit impossible tocatch prey.

name: kabuto
flavorText: A POKéMON thatwas resurrectedfrom a fossilfound in what wasonce the oceanfloor eons ago.

name: kabutops
flavorText: Its sleek shape isperfect for swim­ming. It slashesprey with itsclaws and drainsthe body fluids.

name: aerodactyl
flavorText: A Pokémon that roamed the skiesin the dinosaur era. Its teeth arelike saw blades.

name: snorlax
flavorText: Very lazy. Justeats and sleeps.As its rotundbulk builds, itbecomes steadilymore slothful.

name: articuno
flavorText: A legendary birdPOKéMON that issaid to appear todoomed people whoare lost in icymountains.

name: zapdos
flavorText: A legendary birdPOKéMON that issaid to appearfrom clouds whiledropping enormouslightning bolts.

name: moltres
flavorText: Known as thelegendary bird offire. Every flapof its wingscreates a dazzlingflash of flames.

name: dratini
flavorText: Long considered amythical POKéMONuntil recentlywhen a smallcolony was foundliving underwater.

name: dragonair
flavorText: A mystical POKéMONthat exudes agentle aura.Has the abilityto change climateconditions.

name: dragonite
flavorText: An extremelyrarely seenmarine POKéMON.Its intelligenceis said to matchthat of humans.

name: mewtwo
flavorText: It was created bya scientist afteryears of horrificgene splicing andDNA engineeringexperiments.

name: mew
flavorText: So rare that itis still said tobe a mirage bymany experts. Onlya few people haveseen it worldwide.
